---
title: "_setMinBidUsdValue (BaseAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_zero: minBidUsdValue == 0?
    q_check_zero --> q_revert_zero: minBidUsdValue == 0
    q_revert_zero --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroValue
    q_check_zero --> q_check_same: minBidUsdValue > 0
    q_check_same --> q_revert_same: s_minBidUsdValue == minBidUsdValue
    q_revert_same --> [*]: revert ValueNotUpdated
    q_check_same --> q_update: s_minBidUsdValue != minBidUsdValue
    q_update --> [*]: s_minBidUsdValue = minBidUsdValue, emit MinBidUsdValueSet

    note right of q_check_zero
        INV-001: minBidUsdValue must be non-zero
        INV-002: New value must differ from current value
    end note
